data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT! Welcome Home to 30204 Wilson Street, located in Lake Elsinore, the Dream Extreme Action Sports Capital of Southern California!    The home has NO HOA, Low Taxes, solar, and features 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms with a large, gated, front yard-perfect for entertaining guests while offering a long driveway to park an RV, trailer, or multiple cars. Home sale includes: Washer, Dryer, and Refrigerator as well as seller offering $5,000 IN CREDITS to BUYER TOWARD CLOSING COSTS. This home is conveniently located close to schools, city community parks, shopping centers, and major transportation routes.     Don't miss the chance to make this delightful home with a large front yard your own. It's a rare find that offers the perfect blend of indoor comfort and outdoor freedom.
